This is codfish prepared Nonna Betta style

00:23:57.576 --> 00:23:59.978
and it comes with pistachios and pine nuts

00:23:59.978 --> 00:24:01.769
and I'm not sure what all this sauce is

00:24:01.769 --> 00:24:03.155
but this looks delicious

00:24:03.155 --> 00:24:05.322
and it came bubbling over.

