It should still be very hot.

00:24:11.770 --> 00:24:14.353
As moments ago it was bubbling.

00:24:19.003 --> 00:24:20.895
Yeah, that taste very buttery

00:24:20.895 --> 00:24:23.989
and it has a nutty
flavor from the pine nuts

00:24:23.989 --> 00:24:25.489
and the pistachio.

00:24:26.844 --> 00:24:28.845
And I love those edges of the fish.

00:24:28.845 --> 00:24:33.012
They're slightly caramelized
within this pan as well.

