It's not really tart. Not really sweet.

00:25:25.920 --> 00:25:27.219
It's very pleasant.

00:25:27.219 --> 00:25:30.552
It just goes well with that tender beef.

00:25:34.915 --> 00:25:35.854
That's really good.

00:25:35.854 --> 00:25:37.522
That was a wonderful meal.

00:25:37.522 --> 00:25:39.314
The artichoke was delicious.

00:25:39.314 --> 00:25:41.531
Oh, the pasta was also very good

